Hello everyone,

This is my first Bhop map ever.
If you in any case download this map, please give me feedback - What should be better, what is bad?

This map contains:
- Hard Bhops
- 1 Surf
- Overhand Bhop
- And more.

This is a single bhop map, and it's great!   

Credits:

Jamess (For teaching me some stuff on Hammer)
